SD.3 StructureDefinition-patient-dh-base-1

Base Patient [Draft]

Implementation guidance

No additional guidance is suggested to support implementation of this profile for the expected usage scenarios of this implementation guide.

SD.3.1 Formal Views of Profile Content

The official URL for this profile is: 

http://ns.electronichealth.net.au/ci/fhir/3.0/StructureDefinition/patient-dh-base-1

The purpose of this profile is to provide a base model for the concept of a patient, defining fundamental concepts that form a conforming representation of a patient. It is used as a base model from which to further derive models for specific usage scenarios in an Australian context.

Must Support

In the context of this profile Must Support SHALL be interpreted as follows:

  • The system SHALL be able to include the element when authoring a resource where data is available

  • The system SHALL be able to store and retrieve the element

  • The system SHALL be able to process resources containing the element

This profile builds on AUBasePatient.

This profile was published on Wed Sep 18 11:35:02 AEST 2019 as a draft by Australian Digital Health Agency.
